# Bulk data — images + ChordPro text stay local (and on R2), the rest of the
# dataset is versioned. The .md sheets are distributed via R2 (see
# scripts/upload_md_r2.py) and their presence is baked into the committed
# songs.bin as a `t` flag by build-data.mjs — so the repo never carries 70k
# text files (keeps us under the Cloudflare Pages file-count limit too).
/images
/images-webp
/logs
/data/songs-md
/scripts/.chordpro_cache

# Local-only
.env
.env.local
*.log

# Node / web build
node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local
npm-debug.log*

# public/songs.bin IS committed — it's the XOR+gzip-obfuscated dataset
# Pages serves to the client (decoded in src/lib/songsCodec.ts).

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Unused tesseract language model — the client loads the `eng` model from the
# CDN at runtime (src/lib/chordOCR.ts), so this local ~5MB copy is never read.
eng.traineddata
